{
  "stem": "11205.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was a lot of, you know, Polish people shot, whomever they had a grudge or something.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we used-- my father used to put us on the floor near the window because there was a lot of shooting in between so that it wouldn't hit us.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, four days later, it was-- it was Sukkot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I-- I was in center in the city, and suddenly, people start to scream and run away and hide in the passages in the backyard.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, when I-- we came out-- and Chelm is rather hilly.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All of the streets go up on a-- And then came-- from up the hill came tanks, four tanks, and people start to run [INAUDIBLE] them.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What's happened?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was the first four Russian tanks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Russians came in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And, you know, it was young people, Communists, they must probably knew.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Not that they knew-- they'd been waiting from the outskirts of town, and they've been sitting on the tanks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so it was a very happy occasion.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They went through the whole [INAUDIBLE] straight.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Also, it was collect the Polish army, people which were already, you know, coming from the front going home-- they caught them and made a army-- I think that was [INAUDIBLE] army, because in Warsaw was still fighting.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so when the Red-- when the Red Army came in on the tanks, this-- they had them already-- the Polish army was already on the train to move, and they stopped to shoot to stop them, and they shoot back.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was-- two Russian soldiers were killed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so the whole evening, people were happy.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
